 arch 6\, 13\, 20\, & 27\, April 3 & 10. Register either by calling 707-996
 -5217 or in person at the library's service desk. Please provide a contact
  phone number to receive a confirmation notification. When you receive you
 r appointment date and time\, come to the library as soon as possible to p
 ick up a tax packet. The tax packet includes general information about the
  program\, instructions\, an intake form\, and a list of items to bring wi
 th you. You will only be admitted if you have filled out the required pape
 rwork.
