X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://sonomagymnasticsacademy.com/home/adult-gymnastics-night/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bohemian
SUMMARY:Adult Gymnastics Class
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T183000
UID:260214yYjdHLPrz06cJBX3j168Lw
DESCRIPTION:We’re offering Adult Gymnastics Classes for the 18\\+ crowd!
 \n\nAdult Gymnastics classes occur every Tuesday 5:00 PM to 6:30 PM & Fri
 day from 6:30 PM to 8:00 PM.\n\n$20 per person\, OR pay for a whole 8-we
 ek session in advance through our site. You can attend on Tuesday\, Friday
 \, or both!\n\nPlease bring the class fee in cash at the time of arrival. 
 This can be a DROP IN\, so there is no need to sign up online before comin
 g!\n\nIf you’ve ever wanted to try out gymnastics or get back into it in
  adulthood\, now is your chance! During our adult classes\, open to all ge
 nders\, our coaches will move at the pace of each student\, helping them a
 chieve goals they set for themselves. No experience is necessary to be i
 nvolved in this class\, so this is a great opportunity to learn the basics
  and get some exercise\, no matter what age you are! Try out our trampolin
 e\, bars\, beam\, and other gym equipment in a safe and supportive environ
 ment. You can build strength and increase your range of motion while havin
 g fun like you’re a kid again.\n\nAsk our coaches what you can work on b
 etween classes\, and they’ll help personalize your training!\n\nPlease w
 ear something comfortable and keep long hair tied back. Skirts and restric
 tive clothing are not recommended. You must remove your shoes before going
  onto the mat or using equipment. Please let us know if you have any physi
 cal limitations or health conditions that may interfere with doing certain
  motions. We recommend bringing a water bottle.\n\nYou can email us for mo
 re info or join our mailing list at: info@sonomagymnasticsacademy.com
LOCATION:Sonoma Gymnastics Academy
URL:https://sonomagymnasticsacademy.com/home/adult-gymnastics-night/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian, Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://courses.spiritrock.org/sp/resilience-and-the-open-heart-somatic-practices-for-everyday-stress/", "Press Democrat": "https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/online-resilience-the-open-heart-somatic-practices-for-everyday-stress/18115021/2026-03-13T17"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://courses.spiritrock.org/sp/resilience-and-the-open-heart-somatic-practices-for-everyday-stress/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bohemian
SUMMARY:Online: Resilience & the Open Heart: Somatic Practices for Everyda
 y Stress
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260313T183000
UID:260213RE3iSVDxnUWV4pzQzbRXsw
DESCRIPTION:**with Pawan Bareja\, PhD**\n\nWhen we are out of alignment wi
 th our deepest heart values\, life feels stressful. Whether the trigger is
  personal heartbreak\, economic pressure\, relational conflict\, or the we
 ight of the climate crisis\, the body often reacts with anxiety\, collapse
 \, anger\, or overwhelm long before the mind can make sense of it. You are
  invited to move from stress to love by transforming these patterns throug
 h embodied heart practices.\n\nEach week\, we will begin by gently noticin
 g where activation lives in the body. We’ll then engage in embodied hea
 rt-opening practices to soothe the nervous system and reconnect with inner
  clarity. After practice\, we will re-check the nervous system to observe 
 what has shifted\, revealing resilience as something softly felt\, measura
 ble\, and trainable.\n\nAs the heart opens and the body softens\, many exp
 erience deeper rest\, clearer thinking\, a renewed sense of connection to 
 loved ones\, and the courage to live a more meaningful life.
LOCATION:Spirit Rock Meditation Center
URL:https://courses.spiritrock.org/sp/resilience-and-the-open-heart-somati
 c-practices-for-everyday-stress/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian, Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
