DESCRIPTION:Friday Night Music\, Wine & Dine at Longboard Vineyards\n\nFea
 turing The Refuge Band & Casa Nostra Wood-Fired Pizza\n\nJoin us for a liv
 ely Friday night at Longboard Vineyards in our Barrel Room\, located in do
 wntown Healdsburg\, featuring live music\, award-winning wine\, and handcr
 afted food. Our Music\, Wine & Dine Night pairs the upbeat\, crowd-pleasin
 g sounds of The Refuge Band with delicious wood-fired pizzas from Casa Nos
 tra.\n\nThe Refuge Band brings a fun mix of familiar favorites and feel-go
 od tunes\, creating the perfect soundtrack for a relaxed and social evenin
 g surrounded by barrels and warm winery ambiance. Enjoy Longboard’s wine
 s by the glass or bottle while Casa Nostra serves their signature wood-fir
 ed pizzas\, made fresh on site with quality ingredients.\n\nFriday | 5:00 
 PM – 7:00 PM Free entry\n\nPlease note: This is an over-21 event inside 
 the Barrel Room. Under-21 guests and leashed pets are welcome on the patio
  only.\n\nCome grab a seat early and enjoy a classic Sonoma County night o
 f great music\, great wine\, and great food.\n\nWine available for purchas
 e Live music by The Refuge Band Food by Casa Nostra (wood-fired pizza) Loc
 ation: Longboard Vineyards Barrel Room Address: 5 Fitch Street\, Healdsbur
 g\, CA 95448
LOCATION:Longboard Vineyards
URL:https://www.longboardvineyards.com
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian, Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
