UID:251212_gQjFNjwoE2pPMjPx0hNdQ
DESCRIPTION:Join our beginner salsa class. No experience or partner is nee
 ded. Just comfortable shoes and desire to have fun!\n\nGreat for first tim
 ers!\n\nNo dance experience required\n\nNon-marking shoes soles\n\nNo part
 ner necessary\n\nWe know it can be challenging to learn something new. As 
 such\, the beginner salsa class is geared for people who are starting out 
 or those that are returning to refresh their skills. Our relaxed environme
 nt is perfect for learning salsa basics\, as we make it fun and enjoyable.
  In this class you will learn basic directional steps\, proper frame for p
 artner-work and simple turn patterns. We organize our curriculum so that t
 he movements are easy to remember. Join us to learn the fundamentals! No e
 xperience is necessary and no partner is required. Drop-in fee is $20.\n\n
 Date & Time: Fridays @ 6:30PM – 7:30PM\n\nInstructor: Lucie Ebnerova\n\n
 Address: 4140 Redwood Highway #8 San Rafael\, CA\n\nNote: Arrive 10 minute
 s before. No floor marking shoe soles allowed.
LOCATION: 4140 Redwood Highway #8 San Rafael\, CA
URL:https://salsadancemarin.com/615pm-beginner-salsa-group-lesson/
