 t **both our Windsor and Healdsburg stores.** For just **$10 per child*
 *\, kids can enjoy a hands-on DIY experience where they’ll build seasona
 l projects like March’s Leprechaun Catchers\, April’s garden crafts\, 
 and May’s handmade Mother’s Day gifts. Our team provides all the mater
 ials and guidance needed\, ensuring every child leaves with a sense of pri
 de and a finished project they built themselves. It is a fantastic\, affor
 dable way for kids to learn new skills while parents enjoy a stress-free m
 orning of community and creativity.
