BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://events.vinogodfather.com/roots-man-project-2/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bohemian
SUMMARY:Organizer
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T160000
UID:260210wY14yFDDC0CBHLsSyW1v3w
DESCRIPTION:Roots Man Project plays high energy Roots Reggae dance music! 
 We have shared stages with reggae legends: The Wailers\, Marlon Asher\, An
 thony B\, Jamaican artist Turbulence\, Midnite\, Junior Toots\, Hirie\, E.
 N. Young \\(our music producer\\)\, President Brown\, Tuff Like Iron\, Kav
 a Jah\, Triple Tree\, Arden Park Roots and more. Our non-stop energy can f
 ire up a crowd in no time and it's all feel-good positive vibes! Check out
  the Instagram pages going back to 2014 showing hundreds of happy smiling 
 faces having a great time! Venues: Ace of Spades\, Swabbies on the River\,
  Whole Earth Festival\, Bottlerock afterparty\, Napa Earth Day\, Konocti C
 asino\, Far North Festival and many more. http://www.rootsmanproject.com F
 ood: TBD Misc: Gate opens at noon. Minors welcome\, kids 12 and under are 
 free. Well mannered and well managed puppy dogs are welcome in the outside
  venue area. We will have seating for everyone. Your own comfy folding cha
 irs are welcome. \\*You may bring your own water and "light snacks." \\*\\
 *NO large catering trays\, chafing dishes\, tables\, or other large party 
 supplies allowed. Must coordinate celebrations with venue. info@vinogodfat
 her.com NO outside alcohol of any kind! TICKETS ARE $17 IF PURCHASED ONLIN
 E TICKETS ARE $22 IF PURCHASED AT THE DOOR A $2 ticket fee is included in 
 ticket costs bought online\, at the door\, or over the phone. This helps c
 over ticketing costs and credit card fees. Table Reservation \\(NOT A SHOW
  TICKET\\). Reserving a table is an additional charge and comes with a bot
 tle of wine. A table reservation guarantees a table for you and your guest
 s \\(up to 8 people\\) and a bottle of wine for your table\, but you and y
 our guests must have a GA Event Ticket to enter the event. A Table Reserva
 tion Ticket is $95 plus a $5 processing fee.
LOCATION:Vino Godfather
URL:https://events.vinogodfather.com/roots-man-project-2/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://www.facebook.com/events/1053065303281068/1053065319947733/"}
