DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T140000
UID:250826SgukRVdbF0W8DrhrUvLHkw
DESCRIPTION:A casual weekly gathering. Hang out and draw together! Bring y
 our own pencils\, pens and paper. Limited supplies will be provided. For a
 ll ages and all experience levels. Children must be accompanied by a paren
 t or guardian. Please no ink or paints. The art gallery is open during the
  Drawing Club. Free\, everyone is welcome!\n\nCity Arts Gallery open hours
 :\n\nThursdays 10 a.m. to 2 p.m.\n\nFridays 4 p.m. to 8 pm\\* and until 9 
 pm on 2nd Friday Art Walk\n\nSaturdays 10 a.m. to 2 p.m.
