DESCRIPTION:Meet\, watch\, and talk to cartoonists Wahab Algarmi and Dean
  Stuart. Algarmi was a grant recipient for his comic work Town Force 1 an
 d the Battle for East Oakland. His newest book\, Almost Sunset\, is liste
 d on the School Library Journal’s best books of 2025. Stuart is an autho
 r and illustrator who has been published in Boom! comics\, Darkhorse\, and
  Penguin Random House. His most recent work is the newly published graphic
  novel Cassi and the House of Memories.
