BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://energywavecenter.com/denise-aubin/", "Press Democrat": "https://energywavecenter.com/denise-aubin/"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://energywavecenter.com/denise-aubin/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bohemian
SUMMARY:Reclaim Your Calm A Harmonic Vagus Nerve Reset
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T170000
UID:260214PuftzzbcGEivTcAZ7FInMg
DESCRIPTION:Reclaim Your Calm: Sound\, Breath\, & Flow\n\nJoin us for a un
 ique somatic experience that uses the hypnotic\, melodic resonance of the 
 Rav Vast drum to bathe your nervous system in healing frequencies. Unlike 
 traditional drumming\, the Rav Vast creates a “sound forest” of overto
 nes that helps the mind settle and the body soften. In this session\, we i
 ntegrate: Vibrational Sound Bath: The ethereal tones of the Rav Vast to lo
 wer your heart rate. Somatic Humming: To physically vibrate the vagus nerv
 e from the inside out\, syncing your breath with the drum. Flowing Qigong:
  Gentle\, meditative movements to move “Qi” \\(energy\\) and release p
 hysical bracing in the body. Experience the shift from “survival mode”
  to “serenity.” Denise will guide you through: Qigong to open the body
 ’s energy channels. Humming to stimulate your internal “calm” switch
 . A Rav Vast Sound Bath to wash away tension with beautiful\, resonant har
 monics. Come home to your body. Leave feeling grounded\, peaceful\, and re
 newed.\n\nAbout Denise Aubin\, MQT\n\nDenise Aubin is a certified Medical 
 Qigong Therapist \\(MQT\\) and the founder of Dance of Qigong. She discove
 red Qigong many years ago while traveling her own healing path and has a p
 assion for assisting others on their healing journey back to love. Qigong 
 is all about loving yourself and reconnecting with your joy. Denise loves 
 teaching and empowering others in this ancient art form of self healing ex
 ercises. Denise received her degree from the International Institute of Me
 dical Qigong and received certification as a Medical Qigong Therapist. Den
 ise has been a teacher and healer for over thirty years.
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/denise-aubin/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian, Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
