SUMMARY:Saturday Live Music at Spicy Vines feat. Honey Disposition
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T180000
UID:260206SlYTP0OZqkKDMhrVJGxALw
DESCRIPTION:Where unforgettable wines\, live music\, and good vibes come t
 ogether.\n\nJoin us every Saturday from 3–6 PM at Spicy Vines for a tast
 ing room experience like no other — where top local musicians from acros
 s the Bay Area meet our award-winning small-lot wines. From Rock & Roll an
 d Blues to Jazz\, Bluegrass\, and Americana\, each weekend brings new soun
 ds and new reasons to raise a glass. \n\nHoney Disposition Rooted in frie
 ndship and a shared passion for original songwriting\, Honey Disposition
  blends folk\, jazz\, rock\, and pop into a signature sound that’s hear
 tfelt\, catchy\, and full of soul. \n\nDetails\n\nNo cover. Walk-ins are 
 welcome\, but this event tends to fill up quickly\, so we recommend making
  a reservation. We are dog and family friendly!
LOCATION:Spicy Vines Winery
URL:https://spicyvines.com/event/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian, Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
