SUMMARY:Live Music - The Ukulele Ramblers - Open Uke Jam!
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T180000
UID:260111N3-s9VFDnk-z_ePhluNk4w
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a chill evening of live music and good vibes with 
 The Ukulele Ramblers at our happy hour event!\n\nWelcome to **Live Music -
  The Ukulele Ramblers - Open Uke Jam!** Join us for a fun-filled evening o
 f live music and ukulele jamming at Barrel Proof Lounge. Bring your ukulel
 e and strum along with The Ukulele Ramblers\, a talented group of musician
 s who will be performing a mix of classic tunes and original songs. Whethe
 r you're a seasoned ukulele player or a beginner looking to learn\, this e
 vent is perfect for all music lovers. So mark your calendars for Sundays a
 nd get ready to enjoy a night of great music and good vibes. See you there
 ! Open Uke jam hosted by your friendly neighborhood Ukulele collective.\n\
 nBring your singing voice and your Uke if you've got one\, and enjoy the c
 omfortable\, welcoming space at Barrel Proof Lounge!\n\n21+\n\nLive Music 
 3-6 pm\n\nFree Popcorn!\n\n***www.UkuleleRamblers.net***\n\nCheck out ***
 www.BarrelProofLounge.com*** for all sorts of good times ahead!
