DESCRIPTION:The award-winning barbershop quartet\, Purple Rebar\, has take
 n the barbershop world by storm since their first appearance at the Barber
 shop Harmony Society’s regional contest\, at which they won first place.
  All four singers are current or former members of Chanticleer. Their repe
 rtoire includes classic barbershop hits as well as new arrangements by the
  leading composers of our day\, including the group’s bass\, Jared Grave
 ley.\n\nPurple Rebar is: Tim Keeler\, Andy Van Allsburg\, Jared Graveley\,
  and Kory Reid\n\nSponsored by Marjatta & Steven Daniels\n\nChoral - Progr
 ammed by Sanford Dole\n\nTHE 222 / 222 Healdsburg Avenue / Healdsburg CA
