DESCRIPTION:New Woman and Fox paintings by Teri Sloat celebrate the person
 al journeys we take as we travel outward through landscape trails or inwar
 d through thoughts and dreams. Her ongoing series\, Woman and Fox\, A Jour
 ney\, present rich\, metaphorical paintings that invite you to pause on yo
 ur own path and enjoy the distance you have come.
