  entertaining evening of fun\, and ephemera in a friendly team trivia comp
 etition. Pit your wits against friends and other intelligent life. Show of
 f your astounding knowledge of pop culture\, movies\, music\, sports\, sci
 ence\, literature\, famous faces\, and more. Order delicious food and drin
 ks while you play! Win HopMonk Gift Cards\, fabulous prizes and bragging r
