BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://sonomagymnasticsacademy.com/home/adult-gymnastics-night/", "Press Democrat": "https://sonomagymnasticsacademy.com/home/adult-gymnastics-night/"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://sonomagymnasticsacademy.com/home/adult-gymnastics-night/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bohemian
SUMMARY:Adult Gymnastics Class
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T200000
UID:260214d22vcCOJjUyufhc_k1IWJg
DESCRIPTION:We’re offering Adult Gymnastics Classes for the 18\\+ crowd!
 \n\nAdult Gymnastics classes occur every Tuesday 5:00 PM to 6:30 PM & Fri
 day from 6:30 PM to 8:00 PM.\n\n$20 per person\, OR pay for a whole 8-we
 ek session in advance through our site. You can attend on Tuesday\, Friday
 \, or both!\n\nPlease bring the class fee in cash at the time of arrival. 
 This can be a DROP IN\, so there is no need to sign up online before comin
 g!\n\nIf you’ve ever wanted to try out gymnastics or get back into it in
  adulthood\, now is your chance! During our adult classes\, open to all ge
 nders\, our coaches will move at the pace of each student\, helping them a
 chieve goals they set for themselves. No experience is necessary to be i
 nvolved in this class\, so this is a great opportunity to learn the basics
  and get some exercise\, no matter what age you are! Try out our trampolin
 e\, bars\, beam\, and other gym equipment in a safe and supportive environ
 ment. You can build strength and increase your range of motion while havin
 g fun like you’re a kid again.\n\nAsk our coaches what you can work on b
 etween classes\, and they’ll help personalize your training!\n\nPlease w
 ear something comfortable and keep long hair tied back. Skirts and restric
 tive clothing are not recommended. You must remove your shoes before going
  onto the mat or using equipment. Please let us know if you have any physi
 cal limitations or health conditions that may interfere with doing certain
  motions. We recommend bringing a water bottle.\n\nYou can email us for mo
 re info or join our mailing list at: info@sonomagymnasticsacademy.com
LOCATION:Sonoma Gymnastics Academy
URL:https://sonomagymnasticsacademy.com/home/adult-gymnastics-night/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian, Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"North Bay Bohemian": "https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/intermediate-salsa-class/17159571/2026-03-17T18"}
X-SOURCE-ID:bohemian
SUMMARY:Intermediate Salsa Class
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260317T193000
UID:251213Oz7GSbK_m0ymVIqoMcY_Og
DESCRIPTION:This class is designed for dancers who have a solid grasp of t
 he basics and are eager to expand their repertoire with more complex and f
 luid movements.\n\nPre- requisite:\n\nSalsa Class Beginners\n\nEach week\,
  we’ll break down a new move\, focusing on the technique and connection 
 that will make you a more confident and stylish dancer. We’ll go beyond 
 the foundational steps to cover a wide range of essential intermediate pat
 terns and styling\, including:\n\nTurns and Spins:\n\nMaster your inside a
 nd outside turns\, double spins\, and the elegant 360 and Hand Toss moves.
 \n\nIntricate Patterns:\n\nLearn to execute the 360\, wrap\, as well as va
 rious Cross Body Lead variations like the U-Turn and Spiral.\n\nFootwork a
 nd Styling:\n\nEnhance your rhythm and flair with advanced footwork like t
 he Suzy Q\, Front Tap\, and Mambo Step. We’ll also work on styling with 
 a wrap and improving your posture and upper body movement.\n\nThis class i
 s your chance to refine your technique\, improve your lead-follow connecti
 on\, and add a variety of fun and dynamic moves to your salsa vocabulary. 
 Join us and elevate your dance!\n\nDetails:\n\nNo partner necessary — ro
 tations ensure everyone gets to dance.\n\nPlease wear non-marking shoe so
 les to protect the floor.\n\nArrive 10 minutes early to warm up and get s
 ettled.\n\nDate & Time: Tuesdays @ 6:30PM – 7:30PM
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/intermediate-salsa-clas
 s/17159571/2026-03-17T18
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
