 Ice by Rebecca Connolly May The Travelling Cat Chronicles by Hiro Arikawa 
 June Fried Green Tomatoes at the Whistle Stop Café by Frannie Flagg July 
 The Art Thief by Michael Finkel August My Friends by Fredrik Backman Septe
 mber A Ballad of Love and Glory by Reyna Grande October Happy Wife by Mere
 dith Lavender and Kendall Shores November Medicine Walk by Richard Wagames
 e December Reader's Choice and Potluck  Need a copy? Please call or visit 
