DESCRIPTION:Series 1: Wednesdays\, January 28 – February 18\, 2026\, 6:3
 0 PM – 7:30 PM Series 2: Wednesdays\, February 25 – March 18\, 2026 6:
 30 PM – 7:30 PM\n\nThis Session\n\nEvent Series \\(See All\\)\n\nJanuary
  28\, 2026 from 6:30 pm to 7:30 pm\n\nExperience Level\n\nBeginning\n\nEve
 nt Category: Dance & Movement\n\nAges\n\nAdults\n\n$15 – Single Session 
 Registration Fee $45 – 4 Session Package\\(Available January 28 and Febr
 uary 25\\)\n\nOur Adult Beginner Tap Class is the perfect place to let loo
 se\, learn the basics\, and enjoy the rhythm of tap dance.\n\nAbout the cl
 ass\n\nReady to make some noise and have some fun? Our Adult Beginner Tap 
 Class is the perfect place to let loose\, learn the basics\, and enjoy the
  rhythm of tap dance — no experience necessary! Each week\, you’ll lea
 rn a brand-new mini routine that combines classic steps with modern flair.
  Whether you’re dancing for the first time or returning after years away
 \, this class is designed to be accessible\, upbeat\, and full of energy.
  Come for the tap\, stay for the laughs\, and leave feeling empowered \\(a
 nd a little more rhythmic than before\\). Lace up your tap shoes – it’
 s your time to shine! Note: If you do not have tap shoes\, you can wear so
 cks to the class.\n\nMembership has its benefits\n\nAll Silver Memberships
  and above receive 10% off the registration cost for any purchase over $40
 . Materials fees are not discounted.\n\nBecome a member today and find com
 munity\, connection\, and creativity.\n\nLocation\n\nRoom 213\, Dance Stud
 io
