DESCRIPTION:A relaxed and elegant garden experience! Your host will guide 
 you through a tasting of our Russian River Valley estate wines. In incleme
 nt weather\, this experience will be hosted in our charming tasting room.\
 n\nEnhance your visit with an option to add-on cheese & charcuterie or art
 isanal chocolates to make your wine country experience even more delightfu
