DESCRIPTION:Join us at Encaustic Open Studio\, a monthly workshop designed
  for you to refine your encaustic painting skills under the guidance of k
 nowledgeable instructor Susan Heeringa Piper. Whether you're a beginner o
 r an experienced artist\, this is the perfect opportunity to immerse yours
 elf in the captivating world of encaustic art.\n\nEncaustic painting is an
  ancient technique that involves using molten beeswax and pigments to crea
 te stunning\, textured masterpieces. This unique medium allows for endless
  possibilities\, as it can be layered\, carved\, scraped\, and fused to cr
 eate mesmerizing effects and depth. From ethereal landscapes to abstract c
 reations\, encaustic painting offers a truly immersive and tactile experie
 nce. \n\nBring your own substrate or project to work on\, or start someth
 ing new!
