DESCRIPTION:Come stroll\, shop\, savor\, and soak up the energy of the sea
 son at the debut of Spring by the River Market—our first ever intergener
 ational community marketplace celebrating the Spring Equinox! From sweet t
 reats to artisanal coffee and juices\, painted alebrijes to hand-crafted a
 rtworks and jewelry\, custom bouquets to self-care products\, plus face-pa
 inting\, family portraits\, multi-cultural performances\, and much more! T
 his is just a taste of what Petaluma River Park Foundation and our Communi
 ty Park Designers have in store! Come see how together\, we're transformin
 g the park into a vibrant community experience for all! .fe-block-235ed299
