DESCRIPTION:Live Figure Drawing Every Monday from 6:00pm-9:00pm. This is a
 n uninstructed drop-in session with different models rotating through\, us
 ually in the nude (although sometimes with costumes and props). Poses typi
 cally range from 2 minutes to 20 minutes\, increasing in length. Please br
 ing your own supplies. Tables and chairs will be provided. A limited numbe
 r of tables\, easels\, and drawing horses are available on a first-come/fi
 rst-serve basis. Feel free to bring your own easel or small table if you w
 ould like to as well. Admission at the door is $20. $15 for PAC members &a
 mp\; SRJC students. .fe-block-03e2ed80e38357c0cbe1 {mix-blend-mode: \; }
