 sitions that respond to specific locations and lived experiences. Anderso
 n earned an M.F.A. in Art Studio from the University of California\, Davi
 s\, and a B.F.A. in Painting/Drawing from California College of the Arts 
 in San Francisco.  For more information\, visit SRJC's Agrella Art Galler
 y website! (https://art-gallery.santarosa.edu/exhibition/visiting-artist-
 lecture-series-spring-2026)  You can see more of her work on her website 
 here! (https://www.nicoleireneanderson.com/%C2%A0)
