SUMMARY:Awakening Awareness: Embracing This Moment
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream (CA)\nA session inspired by Eckhart Tolle's
  practices. Feel free to join as we get still and practise presence within
  this moment. We will discuss and observe the obstacles that\, seemingly\,
  block us from being present and bring awareness to our unconsciousness in
  a safe\, inclusive and affirming way.\n\nSessions are suitable for newcom
 ers\, those experienced in Tolle's teaching and anyone wishing to remain c
 ompletely anonymous.\n\nSee you there!\n\nPlease be aware that sessions wi
 ll close if no members have joined after 10 minutes.\n\nEmrys has been pas
 sionate about mindfulness since 2010 and since 2021 he has been organising
  free\, weekly online meditation groups. For more information on his free 
 Work of Byron Katie online mediation group\, visit [this Meetup Group link
 ](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/events/313644290/
