 les\, REM\, Secret Sisters\, Abigail Lapell and many more. Featuring: Bar
 ry Bisson on keyboard\, guitar & vocals\, Tony Blake on drums\, Perry Sav
 as on bass\, Tim Jenkins on guitar\, Mary Lindsay and Carol Oppenheimer o
 n vocals. And as always\, a few special guests!
