SUMMARY:Honoring Ancestry: Celebrating the Artwork of Indigenous Students
  at Santa Rosa Junior College
DESCRIPTION:Exhibit Dates: April 1st - May 31st\, 2026  Opening Reception
  Friday\, April 3rd\, 1:00 - 3:00 pm  This exhibit features both traditio
 nal and non-traditional arts of Indigenous SRJC students from many differ
 ent tribal backgrounds\, including painting\, drawing\, beadwork\, cerami
 cs\, textiles and sculpture. Join us in the Museum on Friday\, April 3rd 
 for a casual reception. Meet the artists and enjoy a light snack.  For mo
 re information\, visit SRJC's Multicultural Museum Website! (https://muse
 um.santarosa.edu/event/honoring-ancestry)
