BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup Contra Dance": "https://www.meetup.com/north-bay-contra-dance/events/313269558/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_contra_dance
X-SOURCE:Meetup Contra Dance
UID:event_313269558@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260309T023559Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T163000
SUMMARY:English Country Dance Sebastopol
DESCRIPTION:North Bay Contra Dance\nEnglish country dancing is done in lon
 g lines (like contra)\, circles\, or in geometric sets (squares\, triangle
 s). Like our contra dances\, there is live music and a caller. You can com
 e by yourself or with friends\, since we change partners after each dance.
  If you’ve ever done contra or square dancing\, much of our dance vocabu
 lary will be familiar to you since both of those styles evolved from Engli
 sh country dancing.\n\nThe dance is held the 1st and 3rd Sundays of each m
 onth\, 2-4:30 pm\, to live music\, all levels of experience welcome\; and 
 occasional 5th Sundays for Advanced dancers. Admission is $15 for members 
 of NBCDS and its affiliates\, $8 for young adults ages 19-30\, and $3 for 
 youth ages 6 – 18.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-bay-contra-dance/events/3132695
 58/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260208T204902Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260208T204902Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup Contra Dance": "https://www.meetup.com/north-bay-contra-dance/events/313269591/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_contra_dance
X-SOURCE:Meetup Contra Dance
UID:event_313269591@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260309T023559Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T213000
SUMMARY:Petaluma Contra Dance
DESCRIPTION:North Bay Contra Dance\nContra Dance is fun\, quick to learn\,
  and great exercise. Every dance night has a live band\, caller\, and a qu
 ick start class for first timers.\nIn contra dance\, you will dance with y
 our partner but also with other couples as you progress down the line. The
  figures for each dance are done in a repeated sequence after a brief walk
  through by the caller. Each dance may last 10 – 12 minutes and then we 
 encourage you to switch partners as the night goes on.\nWhat to wear: Comf
 ortable shoes that will enable you to pivot and slide on the wood floor.\n
 When to arrive: If this is your first time\, come 30 minutes early to chec
 k in\, join the quick start class\, and get you ready for the first dance.
 \nHow hard to learn? Most newcomers will find that they can get dancing ri
 ght away as the figures are quite simple.\nCome as a group\, couple\, or s
 ingle! Our dance is inclusive to all ages and genders.\nCost: $13 members\
 , $15 non-members\, $8 student or limited income.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-bay-contra-dance/events/3132695
 91/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260208T204929Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260208T204929Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
