SUMMARY:Awaken Yoga @ Hotel Petaluma
DESCRIPTION:Nourish 108 Ayurveda & Yoga\nJoin me for 60 minutes of nourish
 ing morning yoga in the serene Brooklyn Ballroom at the Hotel Petaluma. Wh
 ile I am here to offer a sequence of poses\, this practice is yours to giv
 e your mind and body what it needs. Please bring your own yoga mat and any
  props you may need (strap\, block\, bolster\, blanket) and arrive a few m
 inutes early to get situated. Extra mats available for hotel guests.\n\nAl
 l levels welcome!\n\nDrop in is $18\, class passes available\, FREE for ho
 tel guests. Sign up through the calendar at [www.nourish108.com/classes](w
 ww.nourish108.com/classes) or hotel front desk if you are a guest. Pay by 
 credit/debit in advance or cash/Venmo on-site.\n\nI look forward to seeing
  you on your mat!
