UID:9d8ef5c39229fa21f93137f8b04caf3a@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a day of shopping and collecting in beautiful Down
 town Petaluma! Antique and collectible lovers throughout the Bay Area are 
 welcome to come\, browse and shop the 41st Annual Petaluma Antique Faire t
 his Spring on Sunday\, April 26\, 8 am to 4 pm set in one delightful and r
 elaxing setting of Downtown Petaluma. Admission is free. The Faire will be
  located on Kentucky Street\, Fourth Street\, in the A Street parking lot\
 , and on Western Avenue. "The Bay Area's Premier Antique Center\," Histori
 c Downtown Petaluma will transform into an antique marketplace. Amid the b
 eautiful historic buildings\, one-of-a-kind stores\, an incredible array o
 f restaurants and cafes\, guests can find an incomparable selection of aff
 ordable antiques from over 200 dealers. The show has a nice variety of est
 ate jewelry\, linens\, furniture\, art\, kitchenware\, vintage décor\, bo
 oks\, and all kinds of unusual collectibles to suit everyone's budget. Thi
 s show attracts over 8\,000 discerning collectors as well as first-ti
LOCATION:Petaluma\, CA
URL:https://business.petalumachamber.us/events/details/the-petaluma-spring
 -antique-faire-04-26-2026
