SUMMARY:The Environmental Forum - Career Panel
DESCRIPTION:The Environmental Forum is a series of presentations on a wid
 e range of environmental/climate change-related topics for students in co
 urse ENVST 40\, but all students\, staff\, and community members are welc
 ome. Presentations are free and open to the public - choose in-person or 
 on zoom.April29th - Career PanelLocal environmentalists discuss their pat
 hways from college to career and answer questions about their field and t
 heir passions  For more information\, visit the Environmental Forum websi
 te! (https://ess.santarosa.edu/environmental-forum)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The Environmental Forum is a series of 
 presentations on a wide range of environmental/climate change-related top
 ics for students in course ENVST 40\, but all students\, staff\, and comm
 unity members are welcome. Presentations are free and open to the public 
 - choose in-person or on zoom.</p><p><strong>April</strong><strong></stro
 ng><strong>29</strong><strong><sup>th</sup></strong> - <strong>Career Pan
 el<br /></strong>Local environmentalists discuss their pathways from coll
 ege to career and answer questions about their field and their passions</
 p><p>  For more information\, visit the <a href="https://ess.santarosa.ed
 u/environmental-forum" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Environmental Forum
  website!</a></p>
