 ra resources.  Get prepped for finals by finding out what other departmen
 ts have to offer and building your support team on campus.  For more info
 rmation\, visit: https://petaluma.santarosa.edu/workshop-schedule (https:
 //petaluma.santarosa.edu/workshop-schedule)
