  "id": "04dd0147-bbad-44eb-b08a-500f6ca5063e" } ] Cool Petaluma Book Club 
 Our book for May\, Secrets of the Oak Woodlands by Kate Marianchild explor
 es the flora and fauna that inhabit California’s Oak Woodland. It’s po
 ssible that the Oak Woodlands have become commonplace for many of us\, but
  this book exhibits how there are extraordinary creatures so close by. PLE
 ASE NOTE: There are 5 copies at Copperfield’s\; ask for one at the count
 er. Let them know you’re with the Cool Petaluma Climate Book Club. Plus\
 , get 10% off! .fe-block-f0e32d393f079b91f943 {mix-blend-mode: \; } .btn-s
