 peakers\, panelists\, and tabling</strong>\, as they share insight on the
  career journey\, job searching tips\, and how to provide culturally-resp
 onsive medical care that meets the needs of our diverse community. This e
 vent is free and open to all\, funded by the Randolph Newman Cultural Enr
 ichment Endowment Grant\, HOPE\, and Avanzando\, and it will include lunc
 h and live music.</p>
