 r left unsaid\,' turning obsession\, self-destruction\, and malice into p
 otent\, unforgettable hooks. Their music is moody yet danceable—brutal\, 
 honest reflections of the dark\, compelling forces that drive us.\nWho's 
 Cooking: Smash N’ Dash\nWhen: Saturday\, May 10th\, 2-6pm\nWhere: Griffo 
 Distillery & Tasting Bar\nRSVP's are encouraged for this FREE\, All Ages 
 Event. Space is Limited.
