SUMMARY:Celebrate CE 2026
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate CE is a formal ceremony with a processional\, speec
 hes/remarks\, program recognition\, and wrap-up. Programs will be acknowl
 edged\; individual student names will not be called.Deadlines to RSVP: Ap
 r 30 (program) • May 15 (attend)When: Friday\, May 22\, 2026 • 5:00 p
 .m. (arrive by 4:15 p.m.)Language/Access: English/Spanish + interpretatio
 n &amp\; ASL available  For more information\, visit SRJC's CE website! (
 https://ce.santarosa.edu/celebrate-ce-2026)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Celebrate CE is a formal ceremony with 
 a processional\, speeches/remarks\, program recognition\, and wrap-up. Pr
 ograms will be acknowledged\; individual student names will not be called
 .</p><p><strong>Deadlines to RSVP</strong>: Apr 30 (program) • May 15 (
 attend)</p><p><strong>When</strong>: Friday\, May 22\, 2026 • 5:00 p.m.
  (arrive by 4:15 p.m.)</p><p><strong>Language/Access</strong>: English/Sp
 anish + interpretation &amp\; ASL available</p><p>  For more information\
 , visit <a href="https://ce.santarosa.edu/celebrate-ce-2026" target="_bla
 nk" rel="noopener">SRJC's CE website!</a></p>
