 : Pizza 909\n\nWhen: Last Wednesday of EVERY month\, Doors @ 6pm - Trivia
  @ 7pm\n\nWhere: Griffo Distillery & Tasting Bar\n\nThis is a FREE all ag
 es event. RSVP's are encouraged because space is limited. Any minors must
  be accompanied by an adult.\n\n
